rying, it may be necessary to add more corn starch or oat flakes or to remove excess moisture from the batter with a spoon or drain in simmering basket placed in another serving bowl.","<b>Vegetable potato pancakes<b>: replace <b>⅓ of<b> the potatoes with vegetables (e.g. carrots, kohlrabi, cauliflower, zucchini etc.) Double the amount of corn starch and oat flakes. Season with ground pepper and serve with a sour cream herb dip."],"basicInfo":["easy","45m","45m","4 portions"]}